.NET Framework 3.5.name: VRTK_ObjectControl
.NET Framework 3.5.summary: An abstract class to provide a mechanism to control an object based on controller input.
.NET Framework 3.5.remarks: As this is an abstract class, it cannot be applied directly to a game object and performs no logic.
